The most dangerous lies comes in the form of beautifully wrapped gifts.

1.
  in the form of xx 以xx的形式
  form = shape 形态
  
  His family story is told in the form of a play. 他的家族故事是以戏剧的形式来叙述的。
  
2.beautifully wrapped 包装精美的
  There are some beautifully wrapped gifts.
  She is beautifully dressed.
  This is beautifully written.
  
3.gitf-wrapped 包装成礼物的

  Would you like it gift-wrapped?  你要包装成礼物吗？
